Packages:

1. DocBlocker: generates PHPDoc template based on the function --> package:  DocBlockr
	USE: just above function type /** hit enter
	wont auto update if function params changed

2. Annotations: highlight TODO, FIXME, README in comment lines --> package:  SublimeLinter-annotations

3. CodeSniffer: CS implementation for ST3 --> package:  sublime-phpcs
	depends: pear install PHP_CodeSniffer
	optional modules instt. guide: http://www.ivankristianto.com/use-php-code-sniffer-phpcs-sublimetext-3/

4. package --> SublimeLinter

	SublimeLinter-php
	SublimeLinter-jshint need--> npm install -g jshint
	SublimeLinter-csslint need--> npm install -g csslint

5. package --> sftp

6. Anaconda-php: using only phpcpd(copy paste detector), rest functionality same as codesniffer package --> anaconda_php
    depends: package --> anaconda



NOTE: check sublime.settings.user and config file for each plugin
